===Enemy Damage===
Enemy attacking player:
<pre>
Damage = Enemy_ATK - (Player_DEF ÷ 2)
Minimum = 1

Where:
  Player_DEF = Defense (Base + Armor)
</pre>

===Magic Damage===
Magic spells use a modified formula:
<pre>
Magic_Damage = Magic_Power × Multiplier - (DEF ÷ 4)
Minimum = 1

Multipliers by magic type:
  Soul Blade:   ×1
  Flame Ball:   ×2
  Light Arrow:  ×1.5
  Magic Flare:  ×2.5
  Rotator:      ×1 per hit (up to 4 hits)
  Spark Bomb:   ×3
  Flame Pillar: ×2.5
  Tornado:      ×3.5
</pre>

===Critical Hits===
With the Critical Sword equipped:
<pre>
Critical_Chance = Level ÷ 10 (max 10%)
Critical_Damage = Normal_Damage × 2
</pre>

===Elemental Weakness===
When hitting an elemental weakness:
<pre>
Weakness_Damage = Normal_Damage × 1.5
</pre>

