===EXP Gain===
Base experience from defeating enemies:
<pre>
EXP_Gained = Enemy_Base_EXP

With Lucky Blade equipped:
EXP_Gained = Enemy_Base_EXP × 1.5
</pre>

==Stat Formulas==

===HP Calculation===
<pre>
Max_HP = 20 + (Level - 1) × 4

Example:
  Level 1:  20 HP
  Level 10: 56 HP
  Level 25: 116 HP
  Level 50: 216 HP
</pre>

===Attack Calculation===
<pre>
Base_Attack = 2 + (Level - 1) ÷ 2
Total_Attack = Base_Attack + Sword_Attack

Example (Level 20 with Spirit Sword):
  Base Attack = 2 + 19÷2 = 2 + 9 = 11
  Spirit Sword = +20
  Total = 31
</pre>

===Defense Calculation===
<pre>
Base_Defense = 1 + (Level - 1) ÷ 3
Total_Defense = Base_Defense + Armor_Defense

Example (Level 30 with Magic Armor):
  Base Defense = 1 + 29÷3 = 1 + 9 = 10
  Magic Armor = +12
  Total = 22
</pre>

